{"@context":"http://iiif.io/api/presentation/3/context.json","id":"https://digbmc.github.io/pta-manifests/phan/phan-11149/manifest.json","type":"Manifest","label":{"none":["PHAN-11149"]},"metadata":[{"label":{"none":["Timestamp"]},"value":{"none":["1:11:49"]}},{"label":{"none":["Film"]},"value":{"none":["Phantom Thread"]}},{"label":{"none":["Distance"]},"value":{"none":["close-up"]}},{"label":{"none":["Location"]},"value":{"none":["interior"]}},{"label":{"none":["Movement"]},"value":{"none":["fixed"]}}],"summary":{"none":["woman scoops ground up mushroom into tiny vessle"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"homepage":[{"id":"PHAN-11149","type":"Text","format":"text/html","label":{"none":["Object homepage"]}}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1","type":"Canvas","height":1080,"width":1920,"label":{"none":["PHAN-11149"]},"thumbnail":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/tiles/full/300,169/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":169,"width":300}],"items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1/annopage-1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1/annopage-1/anno-1","type":"Annotation","motivation":"painting","target":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1","body":{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/tiles/full/1920,1080/0/default.jpg","type":"Image","format":"image/jpeg","height":1080,"width":1920,"service":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/tiles","type":"ImageService3","profile":"http://iiif.io/api/image/3/level0.json"}]}}]}],"annotations":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1/page/p1","type":"AnnotationPage","items":[{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1/556a723f-37d3-4518-b731-a136edc62452","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:05:18.257Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Ironically, Alma uses a thimble to hold the grated mushroom she will poison him with. She takes a tool used for his craft, the thing that she is not given full access to, and makes it her own, turning it against him. In poisoning Reynolds, she weaponizes the domestic sphere against him in a perversion of the maternal role he has placed her in. After all, it is his tea she poisons, in the kettle he drinks from every morning. What is familiar and soothing becomes hostile, leaving him with no comforts except Alma herself.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:776.3713080168777,380.00000000000006,196.4556962025316,197.80590717299577"}}},{"id":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1/d602850a-e638-49ac-9729-3d81f82495dd","type":"Annotation","motivation":"commenting","body":[{"created":"2026-06-29T19:05:42.491Z","creator":"lucia","purpose":"commenting","type":"TextualBody","format":"text/html","value":"<p>Alma uses a tea infuser to gather the grated and ground mushroom. Given the symbolic weight of tea and teakettles throughout <em>Phantom Thread</em>, her weapon of choice is apt. Other examples of tea scenes include when Reynolds and Cyril pour their tea at the same time in front of Johanna and the tea kettle that stands between Alma and Reynolds when he orders porridge from his kitchen.&nbsp;</p>"}],"target":{"type":"SpecificResource","source":"https://digitalscholarship.brynmawr.edu/pta/phan/phan-11149/canvas/1","selector":{"type":"FragmentSelector","conformsTo":"http://www.w3.org/TR/media-frags/","value":"xywh=pixel:75.61181434599152,97.13080168776372,278.14345991561186,207.25738396624473"}}}]}]}]}